,"grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Mauquf"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Mauquf"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}},{"hadithnumber":3934,"arabicnumber":3934,"text":"","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}},{"hadithnumber":3935,"arabicnumber":3935,"text":"","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}},{"hadithnumber":3936,"arabicnumber":3936,"text":"","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Daif Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif Isnaad Maqtu"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}},{"hadithnumber":3937,"arabicnumber":3937,"text":"","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}},{"hadithnumber":3938,"arabicnumber":3938,"text":"","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}},{"hadithnumber":4938,"arabicnumber":4938,"text":"Uthman bin Abi Al-Walid said:\"I heard 'Urwah bin Az-Zubair say: \"Aishah used to narrate that he Prophet of Allah said: The hand (of the thief) should not be cut off except for a shield or its equivalent in value. And he said that 'Urwah said: A shield is (worth) four Dirhams. And he (the narrator) said: I heard sulaiman bin Yasar say that he heard 'Amrah say: I heard 'Aishah narrate that she heard the Messenger of Allah say: The hand (of the thief) should not be cut off except for four Dinars or more","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan Or Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}},{"hadithnumber":5564.2,"arabicnumber":5564.2,"text":"Qatadah said:\"Anas used to tell us to cut off the extra bits","grades":[],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":0}}]}